---
import Container from "./Container.astro"

---

<div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300" id="reviews">
  <Container>
    <!-- New Section: Opportunities, Benefits, Internships -->
    <div class="mt-20 p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-dark-blue shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10">
      <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-lavender">Opportunities, Benefits, Internships</h6>
      <p class="text-light-purple mt-4">Being a member of YoungMedScholars has numerous benefits, including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-light-purple">
        <li>Receiving letters of recommendation.</li>
        <li>Access to free internship offers.</li>
        <li>Certifications that look impressive to colleges and medical schools.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-light-purple mt-4">Learn about science, medicine, and leadership, with opportunities to apply for executive board positions available to qualifying students worldwide. YoungMedScholars proudly accepts members from 15+ countries.</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center mt-6">
        <img class="w-48 h-48" src="https://i.postimg.cc/T1kgyM7p/logo.jpg" alt="Young Med Scholar Brand Logo" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>

<style>
  .bg-dark-blue {
    background-color: #1a237e; /* Dark blue */
  }

  .text-lavender {
    color: #d1c4e9; /* Lavender */
  }

  .text-light-purple {
    color: #b39ddb; /* Light purple */
  }
</style>
